OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1779624668
OL,3,CTwo men charged in connection with
OL,4,Cdeath of man in Belfast
OL,6,FTwo men have been charged in
OL,7,Fconnection with the death of Nicholas
OL,8,FGordon in east Belfast.
OL,10,FThe 51-year-old, who was also known as
OL,11,FNicky, died in hospital on Saturday
OL,12,Ffour days after an assault in an
OL,13,Fapartment complex on the Holywood Road.
OL,15,FThe men, aged 25 and 31, were arrested
OL,16,Fin Scotland on Monday on suspicion of
OL,17,Fmurder and were transferred to
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
