OL,3,CTwo men charged in connection with
OL,4,Cdeath of man in Belfast
OL,6,FOn Thursday, they were charged with a
OL,7,Fnumber of offences including murder,
OL,8,Fpossession of a firearm with intent to
OL,9,Fcause fear of violence and threats to
OL,10,Fkill.
OL,12,FBoth are due to appear at Belfast
OL,13,FMagistrates' Court on Friday.
OL,15,FA police spokesperson said: "As is
OL,16,Fnormal procedure, all charges are
OL,17,Freviewed by the PPS."
